'''Gillian Libbert''' was the costume supervisor for [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. She has a cameo in ''Attack of the Clones'' as [[Lillea Bringbit]], a patron in the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]]. The character's name is an [[Tuckerization|anagram]] of Libbert's name. She also inspired the name of [[Gilramos Libkath]].

